type: Floor
name: "Crystal Silt"
description: "High-friction crystalline fragments. Its jagged composition slows down mechanical movement."

# Visuals
variants: 4
# Using Harmonic Lavender (#e3b3ff) for the map color
mapColor: e3b3ff

# Gameplay Stats
# A value below 1.0 creates a 'sand' effect, slowing units down.
speedMultiplier: 0.7

# Environmental Attributes
# Crystals are highly conductive and hold a charge.
attributes: {
  heat: 0.2
  charge: 0.4
}